node.text:
The video is hard to watch. Contains animal cruelty. Swipe to see.  We have to do something about this. @animalhopeandwellness 
・・・
This video was taken and posted by an employee at American Canine Academy in Colorado. In the video a trainer is seen strangling a dog, that as a result became unconscious and died. Two other employees are seen in the video, watching and doing nothing to help the dog. 

Several former employees have come forward sharing information of abuse and neglect that has taken place at this facility. Currently, ASPCA has an investigation into the owner Sean Miller — who has denied any wrong doing. 

Commerce Police Department: (303)287-2844. Please call and express your concern. There is a petition in the bio of @kriskellyfoundation

@animalhopeinlegislation
